Instructions:
1. Address the specific issue described
2. Run tests to ensure fix doesn't break anything
3. Document your changes in {{state_dir}}/epics/{{epic.id}}/tickets/{{ticket.id}}/followup-{{followup.id}}.md

The document should include:
- What was changed and why
- How the finding is now addressed
- Any tests added or modified

